data.description:
NOTHING TO DO IN THIS ONE BUT MOVE RIGHT IN! This IMMACULATE ranch home has seen many recent updates, some include freshly painted interior, new doors, newer windows, new trim and crown molding, new plumbing fixtures and new carpeting. The kitchen has new countertops and the appliances are included. The finished basement offers a family room with Blue Flame Heater, an office or possible 4th bedroom and utility room complete with washer and dryer. Nice size fenced back yard with 2 sheds and a private courtyard area. Sellers are providing a 1 year HSA warranty.
